{"tid":1931360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 死亡率絕對唔只3,4個%","createTime":"2020-03-18T06:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T20:44:16.000Z","uid":49910,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0aa4bea0541bdb7cf3043f013a833c6710074a4b","tid":1931360,"uid":49910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:31:51.000Z","msg":"發覺身邊有唔少人都開始鬆懈，尤其啲藍絲廢老開始有論調話死亡率低中咗都唔怕(快啲中唔該), 甚至話中共做得好控制到<br />\n<br />\n加上CCTVB日日用埋啲onl99嘅計數方法，搞到真係有班真心膠覺得死亡率好低冇有怕<br />\n<br />\n如果你身邊都有咁嘅人，唔該你鬧醒佢死亡率係應該用Closed Case去計，即死亡人數/(死亡+康復人數)而唔係坊間嘅死亡人數/確診人數<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3RbPkbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3RbPkbc.jpg&h=52fe89c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果用番上面條式去計你會見到死亡率絕對唔只3, 4%&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n但同藍絲/真心膠講數學即係玩鳩佢，我就會用以下例子，次次都即刻收皮<br />\n<br />\n例一：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你賭波買咗十場波，兩場踢完中咗，另外八場仲踢緊，咁你現刻命中率係咪兩成呀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你都on9嘅，現刻梗係十成啦，中咗就係中咗，你唔俾我另外個八場中埋？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁你知死亡率點計啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n例二<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />. 陳太你個仔考十科，有兩科合格喎，八科未出，咁佢宜家合格率係幾多呀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我個叻仔宜家梗係100%合格啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但至後出咗一科肥咗呢？係咪得番兩成？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你都痴線嘅其他都未出，你又知肥硬？宜家都仲有近七成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁你知死亡率點計啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家要緊記現刻死亡率嘅計法，唔好俾人spin到<br />\n當然最終死亡率同現刻嘅比一定會有出入，因為佢可以受到人民衛生意識，醫療系統，甚至氣候，而產生變化<br />\n<br />\n中共個4%你當睇唔到啦<br />\n<br />\n但你可以留意到醫療體系爆煲嘅意大利，現刻死亡率達高達45.97%，其他歐美國家都係兩成到四成，但南韓全力抗疫加普遍人肯戴口罩都仲保到個醫療系統，再加上本身醫學水平都好，現刻只係有5%<br />\n<br />\n所以唔該宜家鬆懈咗嘅人緊慎番啲，一個唔該食到全球大流行嘅second wave，迫爆我地啲醫院，我估死亡率都係會攀升<br />\n<br />\nThis is not just a flu. This is fucking Chinese Virus."},{"pid":"d2cce94702ed112fdfaa52c18b270ecb59f79638","tid":1931360,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:32:35.000Z","msg":"大陸得2%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5578a28347b01c167c82f02c71180ff12805f122","tid":1931360,"uid":238920,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d2cce94702ed112fdfaa52c18b270ecb59f79638","tid":1931360,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:32:35.000Z","msg":"大陸得2%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:33:40.000Z","msg":"支那同伊朗用緊毅進制唔洗理"},{"pid":"14fe01eefd6109aed35838ea3fb341cdee632c18","tid":1931360,"uid":207217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:36:26.000Z","msg":"成件事未完 都唔會有真正嘅「死亡率」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3411f9a5796205c3fdc48900bd8e83ec9f8edf","tid":1931360,"uid":22624,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5578a28347b01c167c82f02c71180ff12805f122","tid":1931360,"uid":238920,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d2cce94702ed112fdfaa52c18b270ecb59f79638","tid":1931360,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:32:35.000Z","msg":"大陸得2%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:33:40.000Z","msg":"支那同伊朗用緊毅進制唔洗理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:36:56.000Z","msg":"支那係大躍進制"},{"pid":"41ff767e6775087d220e590c1c6964201d75a466","tid":1931360,"uid":49910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14fe01eefd6109aed35838ea3fb341cdee632c18"